original_title: Brooklyn: Portland Avenue S.) - Atlantic Avenue
text:
(1)

127-145 South Portland Ave., east side, north from north of Atlantic Ave., to Hanson Place, showing the Hanson Place Baptist Church at No. 127, at the S.E. corner of Hanson Place. November 26, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)

The same, showing only the church which was dedicated in 1860. This Congregation was organized in 1854. About 1901.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
